med .", "the pair met as undergraduates at st andrews university , fife , before going on to study medicine together at manchester university .", "once qualified , he became a junior doctor at the city 's wythenshawe hospital .", "he was forced to resign following the allegations that he was handing out falsified prescriptions .", "dr osborne declined to comment ."], "summary": ["dr adam osborne 's licence was suspended by the general medical council .", "he has been accused of having an affair with a married psychiatric patient .", "comes five years after suspension for prescribing drugs to prostitute lover ."], "label": [0, 3]}
